# The Lighthouse Keeper's Secret

## The Vanishing Keeper

The storm raged, battering the isolated lighthouse on Blackwood Island.  Old Silas, the keeper, had vanished without a trace. A young journalist, Sarah Jenkins, arrived to investigate, braving the treacherous conditions. "The locals whisper of a hidden treasure," she thought, peering through the swirling rain. “But there’s more to this story than meets the eye.”
